{"tid":166301,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"陷入瘋狂的螺旋中《狂賭之淵》釋出宣傳影片 預計夏季播出","createTime":"2017-03-22T04:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T07:07:23.000Z","uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f110bfabd3bd33f8b78bacd586413d9e4808bd1","tid":166301,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:22:21.000Z","msg":"　由 河本ほむら原作、尚村透負責作畫的《狂賭之淵》，繼日前宣布改編動畫的消息後，官方於今（22）日宣布動畫將於夏季推出的消息，並同步釋出宣傳影片。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/94/0001524194.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F94%2F0001524194.JPG&h=9fc6fc5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《狂賭之淵》故事描述，名門「私立百花王學園」，在這所學園裡存在著階級制度。以學生會為頂點的這一所學校，受到「賭博」支配。贏的話就是天國；輸的話就是地獄。賭博強者受人羨慕、弱者被虐的瘋狂學園。而這樣的學園裡，轉來了一位少女。她的名字是蛇喰夢子&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n <br />\n　　官方於今日釋出的宣傳影片中，雖然大多是以靜態的圖像方式呈現，但藉由原作中各種豐富的表情與台詞，也能讓觀眾先行體會作品世界的瘋狂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/97/0001524197.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F97%2F0001524197.JPG&h=b21f7d10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/96/0001524196.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F96%2F0001524196.JPG&h=a957fdd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Kpaq6EXwSTY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKpaq6EXwSTY&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=1c4aa5d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Kpaq6EXwSTY</a><br />\n顏藝之淵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81eff9264292e9745757869b8efc52a81d2561e3","tid":166301,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"漫畫個作家個畫工真係冇撚得輸"},{"pid":"5981b816ea97c12efff75ade079f35bda6e6087c","tid":166301,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:40:09.000Z","msg":"好想睇主角輸到仆街<img src=\"/assets/fa